OL,3,CMum avoids jail after charging at
OL,4,Cpolice and hurling abuse during protest
OL,6,FA 41-year-old mother has avoided jail
OL,7,Fafter charging at police officers and
OL,8,Fhurling obscene abuse at them during a
OL,9,Fdemonstration in Whitehall.
OL,11,FKelly Wildego, of Greenwich, received
OL,12,Fa four-month suspended sentence at
OL,13,FInner London Crown Court on Monday
OL,14,Fhaving admitted assaulting an
OL,15,Femergency worker.
