OL,3,CMum avoids jail after charging at
OL,4,Cpolice and hurling abuse during protest
OL,6,FAlex Agbamu, prosecuting, said that
OL,7,FWildego shouted at officers "you're
OL,8,Fall a bunch of ******* *****" and "you
OL,9,Fshould be ashamed of yourselves",
OL,10,Fbefore rushing at them saying "*******
OL,11,Ftake me" after most of the violence
OL,12,Fhad stopped at around 8.45pm on July
OL,13,F31.
OL,15,FVideo footage showed her being
OL,16,Fhandcuffed on the ground.
OL,18,FMr Agbamu said this happened in
OL,19,F"isolation" to the earlier disorder
OL,20,Fand "without explanation".
