OL,6,FThe prosecutor told the court that
OL,7,Fduring a police interview, Wildego
OL,8,Fadmitted her conduct and expressed
OL,9,Fremorse.
OL,11,FJudge Freya Newbery handed Kelly
OL,12,FWildego a suspended sentence because
OL,13,Fshe is a full-time carer for her 13-
OL,14,Fyear-old son, who has learning
OL,15,Fdifficulties.
OL,17,FThe judge said Wildego was "nasty"
OL,18,Ftowards officers who were "just doing
OL,19,Ftheir job".
