OL,6,FShe went on: "You're not the sort of
OL,7,Fperson who usually acts like that".
OL,9,FInner London Crown Court had heard
OL,10,Fthat Wildego, who is "wholly ashamed"
OL,11,Fof her actions, got herself arrested
OL,12,Fto be with her husband, who was
OL,13,Fearlier detained by police.
OL,15,FWildego wept in the dock when she
OL,16,Fheard her sentence.
